### Stage5 smoke test via gateway
### Use VS Code REST Client extension or translate to curl

@host = http://localhost:8080
@token = local-demo-token
@plantId = plant-demo-001
@forecastDate = 2026-07-22

### 1) auth session
GET {{host}}/api/v1/auth/session
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2) plant list
GET {{host}}/api/v1/plants?pageNo=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3) system users
GET {{host}}/api/v1/system/users?pageNo=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4) monitor generation list
GET {{host}}/api/v1/monitor/plants/{{plantId}}/generation-records?pageNo=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5) forecast train job submit
POST {{host}}/api/v1/forecast/model-train-jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plantId": "{{plantId}}",
  "startDate": "2026-06-01",
  "endDate": "2026-07-20",
  "featureSetVersion": "feature-v2-xgb",
  "algorithm": "xgboost"
}

### 6) forecast day-ahead submit
POST {{host}}/api/v1/forecast/jobs/dayahead
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plantId": "{{plantId}}",
  "forecastDate": "{{forecastDate}}",
  "modelVersion": "",
  "weatherSource": "api"
}

### 7) forecast list
GET {{host}}/api/v1/forecast/plants/{{plantId}}/dayahead?forecastDate={{forecastDate}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
